# Force-404 internal paths so the strategic brief, design plan, brand assets,
# README, and deploy script can never be fetched publicly.
# The trailing `!` makes the rule force-apply even if a real file exists.
/_research/*    /404 404!
/_design/*      /404 404!
/_brand/*       /404 404!
/README.md      /404 404!
/README         /404 404!
/deploy.sh      /404 404!
/.netlifyignore /404 404!

# SPA-style catchall — must remain LAST.
/*  /index.html  200
